  • public class CycleRemoval
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the cycle removal algorithm from G.DiBattista, P.Eades, R.Tamassia, and I.G.Tollis. Graph Drawing: Algorithms for the Visualization of Graphs, Prentice Hall, Upper Saddle River, NJ, 1999.
